TITLE: Installing Fluent UI React Package
DESCRIPTION: Commands to install the @fluentui/react package using npm or yarn package managers in an existing project.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui/blob/master/apps/public-docsite/src/pages/Overviews/GetStartedPage/docs/web/GetStartedDevelopExisting.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
