TITLE: Implementing Facepile in Fluent UI v8
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the basic usage of Facepile component in Fluent UI v8. It imports necessary components, sets up a number of faces to display, and renders the Facepile with inline and overflow personas.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui/blob/master/apps/public-docsite-v9/src/Concepts/Migration/FromV8/Components/AvatarGroup.stories.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
