TITLE: Construct Scale for Groups
DESCRIPTION: Constructs a band scale (xScale0) to define the geometry of the groups.  The domain is the array of x-axis labels, and the range is the available width, adjusted for margins. The inner padding of this scale is calculated to account for the number of bars in a group and the bar gap rate, therefore ensuring consistent spacing between groups.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui/blob/master/packages/charts/react-charting/docs/implementing-2-to-1-spacing.md#2025-04-20_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: typescript
