TITLE: Equivalent Input Implementation in Fluent UI v9
DESCRIPTION: The equivalent implementation of a basic Input with label in Fluent UI v9. In v9, the Input and Label are separate components that need to be manually associated using htmlFor/id attributes, and styled with makeStyles for layout.
