TITLE: Defining Tooltip Component Interfaces in TypeScript for FluentUI
DESCRIPTION: Defines interfaces for Tooltip and TooltipHost components including props, state, and styles. These components provide contextual information in a popup when users hover over or focus on elements.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui/blob/master/packages/react/etc/react.api.md#2025-04-20_snippet_225

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
