| CI build fails > 50%                                  | ðŸ”¥ Fix ASAP (or notify team if external issue)                                                                      |
| PR builds fail > 50% on non-user errors (CI okay)     | ðŸ”¥ ^                                                                                                                |
| Local builds broken for most/all of team (PR/CI okay) | ðŸ”¥ Fix or at least find workaround ASAP                                                                             |
| Published package broken                              | ðŸ”¥ Fix ASAP (usually due to dep issue or missing file)                                                              |
| CI build intermittently broken                        | âš ï¸ Try to investigate/fix (greater frequency => higher priority), or file an issue if it will take significant time |
| PR intermittently fail on non-user errors (CI okay)   | âš ï¸ ^                                                                                                                |
| Local builds broken for one person/scenario           | âš ï¸ ^ but at least get them unblocked                                                                                |
| v7/8 website release failed (uncommon)                | âš ï¸ Re-run failed stage, or see internal wiki                                                                        |
