TITLE: Calculating Bar Chart Inner Padding Formula
DESCRIPTION: Mathematical formula used to calculate the default inner padding between bar groups. The formula maintains a 2:1 spacing ratio between groups and is based on the space between groups divided by the total of space between groups plus group width.
