TITLE: Creating a Select Component using Dropdown in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases how to create a `Select` component that internally uses the `Dropdown` component from Fluent UI, providing a simplified API for selection. The `Select` component executes the `Dropdown` component with selection capabilities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui/blob/master/packages/fluentui/document-a-feature.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
/**
 * A <Select /> is sugar for <Dropdown selection />.
 * @see Dropdown
 */
function Select(props) {
  return <Dropdown {...props} selection />;
}
```

