TITLE: Using JavaScript state instead of input pseudo-classes in FluentUI
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the preferred approach of using JavaScript state instead of CSS input pseudo-classes for styling. This produces cleaner code with simpler selectors and better maintainability.
