SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui/blob/master/docs/react-v9/contributing/rfcs/react-components/convergence/field-custom-components.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
const MyInputInField = field(MyInput, props => mapMyInputFieldProps(props));

<>
  <Field label="..." validationState="error">
    <MyInputInField defaultValue="..." />
  </Field>
  <Field label="..." validationState="error">
    <div>
      <MyInputInField defaultValue="..." />
    </div>
  </Field>
</>;
```

