TITLE: SlotComponent Type Definition in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the SlotComponent type, which represents the new exotic component type for slots.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui/blob/master/docs/react-v9/contributing/rfcs/react-components/convergence/slot-children-render-function.md#2025-04-20_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
type SlotComponent<Props extends UnknownSlotProps = UnknownSlotProps> = React.ExoticComponent<
  Props & React.RefAttributes<Element>
> & {
  readonly props: Props;
  readonly defaultProps?: Partial<Props> | undefined;
  readonly componentType:
    | React.ComponentType<Props>
    | (Props extends AsIntrinsicElement<infer As> ? As : keyof JSX.IntrinsicElements);
};
```

