TITLE: Demonstrating CSS Class Order Conflict in HTML
DESCRIPTION: This HTML snippet shows how CSS class order can lead to unexpected styling when multiple bundles are involved. It demonstrates the current state where styles from a CDN bundle can override styles from the main bundle.
